{"tid":1656833,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有條友可以令香港人權及民主法案毁於一旦！","createTime":"2019-10-15T20:44:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T23:57:52.000Z","uid":248857,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e2adb440fbb00bf4563541160de010cf2d66cafe","tid":1656833,"uid":248857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T20:44:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NbzCDvm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNbzCDvm.jpg&h=6fe2c728&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">參議院多數黨領袖麥康奈爾（Mitch McConnell）被視為親中派，成為《香港人權法》在參院闖關的隱憂。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其妻子是交通部長趙小蘭，麥康奈爾也曾獲趙氏家族逾<br />\n100萬美元政治捐款。趙氏家族生意被揭跟中國政府過從甚密，趙小蘭也正面臨眾議院調查，質疑她道德操守不妥，甚至有以權謀私之嫌</span></span>。</span><br />\n<br />\n有乜方法？<br />\n<br />\n1.民主黨少數黨領袖舒默（Chuck Schumer）<br />\n<br />\n手握45票既民主黨可以敦促麥康奈爾把法案帶上大會表決<br />\n<br />\n2. 釘緊支持香港既共和黨員，包括所羅門、Rubio、Ted Cruz 同Josh Hawley 既Twitter，並且將戰線重點放係Twitter <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PL9i7nZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPL9i7nZ.png&h=506ed75a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k0H42Wo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk0H42Wo.png&h=319dd010&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.唔好你自己嘅立場，全力支持Gphone！"},{"pid":"9865499564ae9bacb81e9273b3a6f23d2867f70a","tid":1656833,"uid":248857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T20:45:25.000Z","msg":"Push 1/10"},{"pid":"35f77f87bd0f6dc7d4abba76326d54ae68bc58bb","tid":1656833,"uid":248857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T20:45:55.000Z","msg":"Push 2/10"},{"pid":"be88774bcd37a95fd20aad10631e8862b06189d6","tid":1656833,"uid":248857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T20:46:17.000Z","msg":"Push 3/10"},{"pid":"25edc31cc4e5e727fe103db1ff576a2de7593ae2","tid":1656833,"uid":2